Duke Street in Exclusive Bonmarche Talks, Independent Reports

-- B y   B e n   M a r t i n
-- 
2011-06-26T10:59:44Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-26/duke-street-in-exclusive-bonmarche-talks-independent-reports.html
Duke Street Capital Ltd. is in
exclusive talks to buy fashion retailer Bonmarche from Peacock
Group Plc, the  Independent on Sunday reported , without saying
where it got the information.  David Inglis will become chief executive officer of
Bonmarche should Duke Street complete the purchase, the
newspaper said.  -- Editor: Anthony Aarons  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ben Martin in  London  at 
 bmartin38@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
 Paul Armstrong  at 
 Parmstrong10@bloomberg.net . 